<note id="fs-idm168001856" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm196306688"><emphasis effect="bold">Topics</emphasis>: 5.2 Manifest Destiny, 5.3 The Mexican American War</para>
<para id="fs-idm192245184"><emphasis effect="bold">Themes</emphasis>: GEO Geography and the Environment, WOR America in the World</para>
<para id="fs-idm198418384"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objectives</emphasis>: Unit 5B Explain the causes and effects of westward expansion from 1844 to 1877, Unit 5C Explain the causes and effects of the Mexican‚ÄìAmerican War</para>
